#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.82"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.82:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.82:0.2"
msgid "9. Macalavagga"
msgstr "9. Confirmed"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: musāvādīsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.82:0.3"
msgid "82. Musāvādasutta"
msgstr "82. Lying"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.82:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr "“Mendicants, someone with four qualities is cast down to hell."

msgctxt "an4.82:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.82:1.3"
msgid "Musāvādī hoti, pisuṇavāco hoti, pharusavāco hoti, samphappalāpī hoti—"
msgstr "They use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical."

msgctxt "an4.82:1.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ "
"niraye."
msgstr "Someone with these four qualities is cast down to hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.84"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.82:2.1"
msgid ""
"Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge."
msgstr "Someone with four qualities is raised up to heaven."

msgctxt "an4.82:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.82:2.3"
msgid ""
"Musāvādā paṭivirato hoti, pisuṇāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti, pharusāya vācāya "
"paṭivirato hoti, samphappalāpā paṭivirato hoti—"
msgstr "They don’t use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical."

msgctxt "an4.82:2.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ "
"sagge”ti."
msgstr "Someone with these four qualities is raised up to heaven.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.82:2.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
